    "body": "So how it should work? Firstly i send tx. Then after some time i should check whether the tx completed or not. If not then i should replace tx. Then i should wait and check again. And it may repeat time after time. All that time i can't send any another tx. So all other users on my website should wait till only one tx will be fulfiled. It works like prehistoric single-threaded application.\r\n\r\nSo the only decision is to track nonce and txs by myself. But [nobody knows how to do it](https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/issues/23023#issuecomment-864065882).\r\n\r\nI'm tired trying to fix all that errors i encountered since decided to work with Ethereum. You have developed piece of junk!",
